Package com.asemantics.rdfcoder.model

This package defines the RDF Code Model and the query facilities.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Asset An asset represents a logic set of related libraries.
BackTrackingSupport This class extends CodeHandler to provide a back tracing mechanism able to accept unresolved types and fix it in a second time.
CodeHandler Defines a tode handler, that is a class able to process parsing events and backtracking support.
CodeModel Defines the Code Model, that is a graph representing the Kabbalah model.
CoderFactory<T extends CodeHandler> Factory class allowing the creation of main library objects.
ErrorListener Error listener meant to collect errors and warnings occurred during the parsing process.
ParseHandler Defines the interface exposed by a Parse Handler, that is the handler receiving messages from a CodeParser.
QueryModel Represents a model to query the CodeModels.
QueryResult Defines the result object of a SPARQLQuerableCodeModel.
TripleIterator Defines an iterator over triples.
 

Class Summary
CodeModelBase Contains base methods common to every Code Model.
Identifier Defines the unique context of a resource.
IdentifierBuilder Helper class used to build the current parsing context.
IdentifierBuilder.IdentifierBuilderInstance  
IdentifierFragment Represents the fragment of an Identifier of a resource.
IdentifierReader This class provides facility methods to read a context built using the IdentifierBuilder.
SPARQLQuerableCodeModel Represents a CodeModel exposing a SPARQL endpoint.
 

Exception Summary
CodeHandlerException Exception raised by the JavaCodeHandler.
CodeModelDebugException Defines an exception raised by a CodeModel implementation whilst a debug control fails.
CodeModelException Exception raised by CodeModel when a generic error occurs.
QueryModelException Defines any exception raised by the QueryModel.
SPARQLException Exception raised by SPARQLQuerableCodeModel if any error occurs during the execution of the SPARQL query.
 

Package com.asemantics.rdfcoder.model Description

This package defines the RDF Code Model and the query facilities.
